## Start Project

When Jon says **Start Project**, **Begin Project**, **Start Session**, or **Cold Start**:

- Execute [`.cursor/prompts/Start-Project.md`](../prompts/Start-Project.md)
- Run **`npm run session:start`** (add **`:full`** to also pre-warm OmniVoice)
- Read `TRUTH.md`, `.cursor/docs/START-HERE.md`, `.cursor/docs/ReCall.md`
- Speak the greeting once via **`npm run jarvis:speak -- "..."`** (ritual-only)
- Handshake: **"Ok Jon â€” JONBEATZ.DEV site loaded, ready."**

## End Project

When Jon says **End Project**, **End Session**, or **Close Session**:

- Execute [`.cursor/prompts/End-Project.md`](../prompts/End-Project.md)
- Update `.cursor/docs/ReCall.md` and `.cursor/docs/project-log.md`
- Short farewell via **`npm run jarvis:speak -- "..."`** (ritual-only)
- Run **`npm run session:stop`** (also stops the OmniVoice daemon)

## Update Docs

